    "headline": "KKR Closes Acquisition of Arctos Partners",
    "summary": "NEW YORK, May 05, 2026--KKR & Co. Inc., a leading global investment firm, today announced that it has closed its previously announced acquisition of Arctos Partners (\"Arctos\"), a premier institutional investor in professional sports franchise stakes globally and a leader in asset management solutions for sponsors. The transaction has received the specified sports league approvals required for closing.",
